WEBVTT

00:01:59.720 --> 00:02:01.820
and how could you exist without them?

00:02:01.844 --> 00:02:03.830
You couldn't! So, you don't.

00:02:03.854 --> 00:02:05.819
Life is but a dream,

00:02:05.843 --> 00:02:10.270
and I bet you aren't row, row,
rowing the boat merrily at all, are you?

00:02:10.294 --> 00:02:11.939
No, you're rowing it wearily

00:02:11.963 --> 00:02:17.205
like the duped, nonexistent
doof you are/aren't.

00:02:17.229 --> 00:02:18.778
Do you find that convincing?

00:02:18.802 --> 00:02:20.049
Are you persuaded?

00:02:20.073 --> 00:02:23.236
If you aren't, good;
if you are, even better,

00:02:23.260 --> 00:02:25.205
because by being persuaded,

00:02:25.229 --> 00:02:28.283
you would prove
that you're a persuaded being.

00:02:29.132 --> 00:02:31.749
You can't be nothing
if you think you're something,